node.text:
Save & Share this Easy Move! 💾

Made by using the spotlight mode 💡

Camera Settings:

4k 30fps - 1/80 - ND16 - ISO 100 - WB 5700K
10bit - D Cinelike

Export:

H.265 - 1080p - MP4

Shot on @djiglobal mini 3 pro 🚁

Follow my page for more! 🚀

#droneoftheday #djimini3pro #drone #dronetutorial #cinematicsettings #cinematicdrone #droneshot #dronereel #dronebeginner #djicreator #djimini4pro #djiflip #djineo #djimavicair #djimavic3pro #videography #tutodrone
@mintadventures_ It's throttle up a bit left and left stick up and a bit in the right (mode 2) make sure to use the spotlight mode to assist you with the tracking 😁 ↖️➡️
Great but i cant really see your moves with sticks/ controllers; i think ↘️↗️➡️↙️↖️⬅️⬇️⬆️ would help a lot🙏🙏🙏
@its.styam Will restart a set of cinematic drone tutorials, stay tuned 😉
I’m more impressed by how you film your controller while holding it with 2 hands 😆
Tell us about your settings for the shot please
@mikph21 YES I will definitely prepare a new set of tutorials ;)
Need more video like this please 🙏
Would love to see this type of tutorial videos in your up coming reels. Plzz continue doing it, it's very helpful.
Hey ! Dans le Vallon de l’Aubonne !
@vdm340 Work smarter not harder haha but in reality I still prefer to do the moves manually since sometimes tracking sucks
@droey.fpv honestly I like it but the stuff I shoot wouldn't be useful. The video is awesome though
Here I am doing everything manually without tracking and everyone else is cheating😂
